narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Continuation of 132, not much different. Class experience depends on the people in the class.
lots of work, helpful in learning Hindi

I definitely would recommend Hindi 142. Just make sure you do Hindi 132 so that you have a good idea of the level involved and how it differs from the other L3 Hindi class. If you are someone who requires rigorous grammatical training (lots of drills/exercises), then you'll be better of in the regular L3/L4. If you are comfortable enough with the language to focus on conversation, writing opinion pieces and essays and 12-15 sentence skits, then definitely take Hindi 132/142.
